data.title: The Fox and the Hound, Oliver and Company and The Aristocats (3 Disney VHS Movies)
data.meta_description:
Taken from an local Savers store of Manchester, CT today. There is about 3 Disney VHS Movies for Everyone. If you are an DIsney movie fan, This is an great chance of your collection 
	
	The Aristocats (1970) -- Disney's 20th animated film -- starring Phil Harris as Thomas O'Malley and Eva Gabor as Duchess
	The Fox and The Hound (1981) -- Disney's 24th animated film Based on the book by Daniel Mannix and then, turning into an Disney animated film
	Oliver and Company (1988) -- Disney's 27th animated film -- starring Billy Joel as Dodger and Joey Lawrence as Oliver
